gitbook depend on npm.
npm can not touch in China.
So, in china , gitbook install steps like this:

1 install node
     
2 install cnpm
   how to install cnpm ?
   <1>open cmd, using administrator.
   <2>run this statement: npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org
   
3 install gitbook-cli
    how to install ?
    <1>go to a place that you can sucess ping 114.55.80.225.
    <2>run thisï¼š cnpm install -g gitbook-cli
      
4 install gitbook
     run this: gitbook -v
     
It's all. :>
